        "title": "fix(qa): reduce WhatsApp live RTT setup cost",
        "body": "Summary\n- Skip WhatsApp live QA agent workspace bootstrap and force exact-marker canaries to run with thinking disabled in both defaults and per-model params.\n- Add per-scenario WhatsApp live timings, RSS samples, complete heap snapshot capture, and redacted gateway trace artifacts.\n- Skip eager participating-group metadata hydration for DM-only WhatsApp sessions.\n- Add changelog coverage for the QA and WhatsApp runtime changes.\n\nVerification\n- `node scripts/run-vitest.mjs extensions/qa-lab/src/live-transports/whatsapp/whatsapp-live.runtime.test.ts`\n- `node scripts/run-vitest.mjs extensions/qa-lab/src/live-transports/whatsapp/whatsapp-live.runtime.test.ts extensions/qa-lab/src/live-transports/shared/live-gateway.runtime.test.ts`\n- `node scripts/run-vitest.mjs extensions/whatsapp/src/monitor-inbox.behavior.test.ts`\n- `node scripts/run-vitest.mjs extensions/qa-lab/src/live-transports/whatsapp/whatsapp-live.runtime.test.ts extensions/whatsapp/src/monitor-inbox.behavior.test.ts`\n- `git diff --check`\n- Testbox-through-Crabbox `tbx_01krx90szx6z16pqh37w0206tf`: scoped `pnpm check:changed -- <touched paths>`, exit 0\n- Testbox-through-Crabbox `tbx_01krx9ne1a4egr0qxpp22chkf5`: scoped `pnpm check:changed -- <touched paths>`, exit 0\n- Testbox-through-Crabbox `tbx_01krxagz91ep6d1ca29qx5b00q`: scoped `pnpm check:changed -- <touched paths>`, exit 0\n\nLive evidence\n- `26027068186` at `fdc2d0e9`: WhatsApp job passed; RTT `7532ms`; trace isolated ~`5141ms` in agent/model before outbound send.\n- `26027596921` at `74c4bb73`: WhatsApp job passed; RTT `7930ms`; trace isolated ~`5890ms` in agent/model before outbound send.\n- `26028278115` at `9ef7fbe1`: WhatsApp job passed; RTT `10393ms`; trace isolated ~`7129ms` in agent/model before outbound send.\n\nBehavior addressed: WhatsApp live QA canary artifacts now separate channel/provider cost from agent/model cost, capture complete heap snapshots, and avoid unnecessary setup/group hydration in the DM-only path.\nReal environment tested: live WhatsApp Convex QA on GitHub Actions, plus Blacksmith Testbox-through-Crabbox changed gates.\nExact steps or command run after this patch: `pnpm openclaw qa whatsapp --provider-mode live-frontier --model openai/gpt-5.5 --alt-model openai/gpt-5.5 --scenario whatsapp-canary` through `qa-live-transports-convex.yml`.\nEvidence after fix: WhatsApp provider-path trace is now visible; the latest run shows inbound/provider/outbound overhead is small compared with agent/model time.\nObserved result after fix: this branch improves observability and removes some setup work, but it does not yet reduce the live canary into the target range; current dominant cost is agent/model pre-outbound latency.\nWhat was not tested: full workflow green is not claimed; the exact workflow runs may show unrelated lane failures after the WhatsApp job/artifact succeeded.\n",
